FBIS3-51403 "drlat012_a_94009" FBIS-LAT-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Chile Approves Special Line of Credit FL1501013594 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 0000 GMT 15 Jan 94 FL1501013594 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Enrique Correa Rios, Chilean minister secretary general of government, today in Santiago, Chile, announced that a special line of credit for Cuba was approved today by the National Bank of Chile. The line of credit, in the amount of 17 million German marks, approximately $10 million, will be used to purchase food. Correa said he believes this operation will benefit Chilean producers. Correa also stressed President Patricio Aylwin's participation in the approval of the credit given Cuba.
